September 2014, Utah - A beautiful young woman in the prime of her life disappears. She is last seen by a surveillance camera near her condo. Police say she was behaving strangely leading up to the time she went missing. This week we share a few beers and give our opinions as we take a deep dive into the case of Kayelyn Louder.
